  "prompt": "Who is the best mobile in 2016?",
  "response": "In 2016, one of the top-rated mobile phones was the **Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge**. It was widely praised for its impressive design, excellent performance, and innovative features. Here are some key highlights:\n\n- **Display**: 5.5-inch Quad HD Super AMOLED\n- **Processor**: Exynos 8890 or Qualcomm Snapdragon 820 (depending on the region)\n- **Camera**: 12MP rear camera with dual-pixel autofocus, 5MP front camera\n- **Battery**: 3600mAh with fast charging and wireless charging capabilities\n- **Storage**: 32GB internal, expandable via microSD\n- **Other Features**: Water-resistant (IP68), curved edge screen for additional functionality\n\nAnother strong contender from 2016 was the **iPhone 7 Plus** by Apple, known for:\n\n- **Display**: 5.5-inch Retina HD\n- **Processor**: A10 Fusion chip\n- **Camera**: Dual 12MP rear cameras (wide-angle and telephoto), 7MP front camera\n- **Battery**: Up to 21 hours of talk time\n- **Storage**: Options ranging from 32GB to 256GB\n- **Other Features**: Water-resistant (IP67), introduction of the dual-camera system for better zoom and portrait mode\n\nBoth phones received high acclaim and were among the best choices for consumers in 2016. The best phone for you would depend on your specific needs and preferences.",
